duplicate

Find all duplicate files in a directory and optionally delete them

Speed

$ find ~/dir/ -type f | wc -l
4698
$ time duplicate ~/dir/ >/dev/null
real	0m 0.78s
user	0m 0.10s
sys	0m 0.68s

Examples

# find all duplicates
$ duplicate ~/dir/
rm /home/exa/dir/file.png # /home/exa/dir/copy1/file.png
# delete all duplicates
$ duplicate ~/dir/ | sh

dependencies

- uthash
- xxhash
